            "title": "名词解释",
            "date_published": "2025-09-02T13:46:05.000Z",
            "content_html": "<h1 id=\"名词解释\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#名词解释\">#</a> 名词解释</h1>\n<ol>\n<li>PCBA(Printed Circuit Board Assembly)<br />\n印刷电路板组装件，将电子元件通过焊接工艺固定到PCB上的成品</li>\n<li>PCB(Printed Circuit Board)<br />\n印刷电路板，由绝缘基材、导电线路和焊盘组成的三维结构载体</li>\n<li>PDM(Product Data Management)/PLM(Product Lifecycle Management)</li>\n<li>CIS(Component Information System)<br />\ncadence 元器件库管理</li>\n<li></li>\n</ol>\n",
